ActorNotificationUnreadNotification is a List
    title is "Notifications"
    Display Fields
        create stamp
            sort order is ByActorCreated
                is default descending
        Description
        SourceType
        Priority
        Details
        Status
    Instance Selection
        where (Actor = actor
        and   Status.Unread)
    open action is Redirect
    open action is Update
    restrict action PurgeNotifications
    restrict action PurgeNotificationsForActor
    restrict action PurgeNotificationsWithDeleted
